---
title: Greek Ragù with Almonds, Eggplant and Basil Couscous
description: Greek ragù is one of the lesser known treasures of Aegean cuisine. The gentle, warm tang of tomatoes blends like a charm with almonds and eggplants. And when you add the flavourful basil couscous into the mix, well, take our word for it, everyone will love it!
